## Setup

```bash
mise install                  # terraform + tflint + pre-commit, pinned
mise run bootstrap            # install git hooks
mise run validate             # init (no backend) + validate
```

Common tasks: `mise run fmt` · `mise run lint` · `mise run plan`.

State and `*.tfvars` hold secrets and are gitignored — configure the backend and
provider for your environment.

